query:
INSERT INTO subjectEnrollments (studentId, subjectId, userId, status)
SELECT 
  (SELECT id FROM students WHERE registrationNumber = '2024001') as studentId,
  lm.subjectId,
  lm.userId,
  'active'
FROM learning_modules lm
GROUP BY lm.subjectId, lm.userId
LIMIT 1;
